p beyond the text."},{"id":"D","text":"It can be inferred that these larvae would eventually molt successfully if researchers extended the observation period by several additional weeks at the same temperature. according to the specific.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Reverse Conditional] Equivocation: It can be inferred that these larvae would eventually molt successfully … cannot be proven solely from the premises given."}]'::jsonb, 'C', 'Step 1 — Identify stated logic
