 who recalled word lists accurately must have slept eight hours before every retrieval test in the study.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Reverse Conditional] Speculative Narrative: It can be inferred that participants who recalled word lists accurately … cannot be proven solely from the premises given."}]'::jsonb, 'A', 'Step 1 — Identify stated logic
