emises given."},{"id":"D","text":"It can be inferred that students who cited textual evidence during disagreements must have been assigned worksheet-only instruction before joining pair discussions.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Reverse Conditional] Speculative Narrative: It can be inferred that students who cited textual evidence during disag… cannot be proven solely from the premises given."}]'::jsonb, 'A', 'Step 1 — Identify stated logic
