rginal notes and tariff records are equivalent proof that every scientific text was copied solely for commercial tax assessment.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Reverse Conditional] Reverse Conditional: It can be inferred that marginal notes and tariff records are equivalent… cannot be proven solely from the premises given."}]'::jsonb, 'B', 'Step 1 — Identify stated logic
